            <h2>What is Local SEO?</h2>
            <p>Local SEO focuses on improving visibility for searches with local intent. When someone searches for "plumber near me" or "cafe in Surry Hills," local SEO determines which businesses appear in those results.</p>
            <p>Local search results differ from standard organic results. They often include map listings, business information panels, and results weighted toward geographic proximity to the searcher.</p>
