            <h2>How Local SEO Works</h2>
            <p>Local search ranking depends on three primary factors: relevance, distance, and prominence.</p>
            <ul class="content-list">
                <li><strong>Relevance:</strong> How well your business matches what the searcher is looking for</li>
                <li><strong>Distance:</strong> How close your business is to the searcher's location or the location specified in their search</li>
                <li><strong>Prominence:</strong> How well-known and authoritative your business appears online</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Local SEO work addresses all three factors through business listing optimisation, citation building, review management, and local content development.</p>
